Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:06.56,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I think I’ll go for a dip\Nin the outdoor bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.91,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.71,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I’m coming to be "killed."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:51.08,B2,REAPER A,0000,0000,0000,,Drive it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:52.64,B2,REAPER B,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll drive it away from the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:11.93,B2,SQUAD NINE REAPERS,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.32,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Were any of the townspeople injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:14.28,B2,REAPER A,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.28,0:02:15.01,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:16.55,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll let you handle it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:18.07,B2,REAPER A,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:21.25,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,To my next job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:29.08,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}“Editor-in-Chief”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:29.08,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai hasn’t turned\Nin his manuscript?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.32,B2,EDITORIAL STAFF C,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:31.17,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Have you contacted him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.73,B2,EDITORIAL STAFF C,0000,0000,0000,,We haven’t been able to reach\Nhim since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.51,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.66,B2,EDITORIAL STAFF C,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:39.05,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s our job to figure that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.09,B2,EDITORIAL STAFF C,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.65,0:02:43.79,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,For now, go to Squad Six's Barracks\Nand see how he’s coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:44.70,B2,EDITORIAL STAFF C,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:48.40,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they’re all useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.82,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I see you’re busy as\Nalways, Hisagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:56.07,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, I’m sorry. Mind\Nwaiting a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:59.29,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I’m not in any hurry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.94,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, send this to the printer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:03.85,B2,EDITORIAL STAFF D,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:10.79,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Now then… So this is the Men’s Soul Reaper\NAssociation’s budget for this term?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:13.61,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think there are any issues\Nwith anything in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.06,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,so please put your stamp\Nof approval on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:18.74,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,As an officer of the association,\Nyou know I can’t do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.31,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m telling you, it’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:23.83,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,The Vice-Chairman, Third Seat Iemura,\Nis a very meticulous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:25.80,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:28.27,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,There don’t seem\Nto be any issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:30.52,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}“APPROVED”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.38,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:34.01,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I’ll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.26,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:38.78,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s been a while.\NWhat do you say we go for a drink tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.02,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be happy to join.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:44.19,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Any seats available?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:46.39,B2,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Wait just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.46,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,If it isn’t Lieutenant Hisagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:53.54,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Unohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.50,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.96,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,It’s ladies' night out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:58.92,B2,HISAGI/KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:03.89,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:07.38,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,I haven’t yet thanked you for the\Nother day, Lieutenant Hisagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:10.34,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanked you? Did you\Ndo something, Hisagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:15.35,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when we all went on a\Npicnic, he made lunch for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.56,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:21.19,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it,\Nbut I’m a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.56,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,It was a 60 out of a 100 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:26.70,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,The meal was ordinary.\NIt lacked creativity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.59,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,It needed more…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.16,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kusajishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:30.95,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,We’re sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.37,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,It tasted all right, honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:35.85,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,“All right,” eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:39.24,B2,UNOHANA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we must be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.21,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:42.25,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let’s get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.52,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let’s!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:45.58,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies' night out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.36,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose they\Nwere talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:54.20,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi, you take on\Ntoo much work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.09,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,You’re busy enough already\Nbeing a Squad Lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.71,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,and running the Seireitei Bulletin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.00,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Why accept the Executive\NChairman position
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.38,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,for the Men’s Soul Reaper Association?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.93,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t mind. I do it\Nbecause I enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.62,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,No, it’s not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:13.33,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you making lunch for the\NWomen’s Soul Reaper Association, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:18.40,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…because they depended\Non me. What was I to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.10,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not easy being\Na talented man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:26.06,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll bet you did it to get Matsumoto’s\Nattention, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:28.26,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:33.39,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Work isn’t something you\Ndo for its pros and cons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.13,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if you do your best,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:38.90,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,there’ll always be someone\Nwho will take notice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.57,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:46.77,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,You sure it’s not just them\Ntaking advantage of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:47.85,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:51.09,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Can we\Nget another bottle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:52.41,B2,WAITRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:58.24,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,And therefore, in order to\Nsolve the disappearances
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:01.01,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,that have been occurring\Nin the Rukon District,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.55,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,it’s been decided that you three\Nwill be sent to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.34,B2,RANGIKU/HISAGI/ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.35,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,So I get to be the leader\Nof this group, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.35,0:06:10.33,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:15.25,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But no matter how you\Nlook at it, I’m the leader here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:18.10,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,How did you come to\Nsuch conclusions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.24,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hisagi, keep an eye on Matsumoto\Nto make sure she doesn’t
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.73,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,do something crazy on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:23.72,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:24.15,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:26.41,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, that’s mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.54,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,When do I ever do crazy\Nthings on my own?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.61,B2,HITSUGAYA,0000,0000,0000,,Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:32.20,B2,ISANE,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, Rangiku. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:35.86,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Captain Hitsugaya put\Nhis trust in me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:39.68,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People do take notice of one’s\Nhard work. I knew it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:59.21,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, the captain can be so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:03.14,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,The skies are looking like rain,\Nso we’d better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:07.94,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I’m a bit tired.\NLet’s rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.88,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,You rested just a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.62,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,We’re almost at our destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.96,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,and it’ll be difficult to move\Nonce the sun sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:21.54,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I wish I could’ve come later\Nwith Isane and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:25.81,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kotetsu is leading\Nthe rescue party,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.34,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,so she has a lot of material\Nand people with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.50,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why we’re\Ngoing on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.72,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:34.88,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:35.76,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.83,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:58.59,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,If we’re in the field shown\Non this map,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:02.71,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,then our destination is somewhere\Naround here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.02,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:08.08,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll take time for Isane and her group\Nto catch up with us anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:11.86,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,so let’s take our time to look around\Nand investigate along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.38,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I think the rain has stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.67,0:08:24.59,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:33.10,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei, stop looking so serious over\Nthere and take a look around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.78,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:39.94,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a second. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:43.92,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We’re in the boonies of the\NRukon District with no one around. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:49.25,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it possible that Rangiku is\Nenjoying her time alone with me? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:52.24,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that smile… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.23,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, Shuhei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:06.45,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no… Nothing wrong, ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:10.62,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop thinking silly thoughts,\NShuhei Hisagi! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:14.23,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow… Sure is a soothing\Nsight for the soul, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:16.85,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:17.20,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.79,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.01,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it’s a lovely landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:33.84,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is. We’ve kept this landscape\Nthis way for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.64,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:39.71,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:41.22,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.34,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from these parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:46.77,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I run an inn over that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.35,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:53.25,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say, Shuhei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:55.35,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Since we’re here,\Nwant to spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:56.46,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:58.14,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,You have a room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:09:58.86,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.41,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.95,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn’t be right, Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.32,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, what’s the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.46,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to be here on a mission anyway.\NWhat’s wrong with staying at an inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.58,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to sleep outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.30,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.98,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Show us the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:15.59,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.52,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go! Shuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.76,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:29.82,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Wow…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.88,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a nice room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:40.86,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:44.55,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Let me make your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:46.40,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:47.27,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:48.72,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay, I don’t mind doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:54.86,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,We’re guests here, so why\Nnot let her make the tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:55.78,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:56.70,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Let her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.70,0:10:58.21,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.42,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What’s gotten into Rangiku? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.10,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could she be jealous? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:10.59,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that I think about it, when the proprietress\Nand I first started talking, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.90,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she suddenly wedged\Nherself in. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:17.56,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, but… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:20.37,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei, why are you so out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:22.08,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Have some tea, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:22.91,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.21,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.61,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:28.45,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.23,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.72,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Was the cup too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:32.88,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.88,0:11:34.55,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:37.68,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,I see… My sincerest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:40.13,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! We have to cool it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.88,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.88,0:11:43.12,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Um… No…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:45.40,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Proprietress, could you\Nget us some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.33,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:56.61,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… Rangiku, your…hand, it’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:00.90,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei, you mustn’t let your guard\Ndown with that proprietress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:01.75,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.32,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Just do as I say, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.35,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:10.50,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought, Rangiku is conscious\Nof the proprietress. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.52,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means, she thinks of me as…  {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.91,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Whew! I'm so full!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:25.54,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’s the matter?\NYou weren’t hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:27.80,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,No, that’s not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:31.88,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Drat. I was so conscious of her\Nmy food wouldn’t go down.  {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:34.16,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,You need to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:36.62,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, you won’t be of use\Nwhen trouble occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.77,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.79,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,You won’t be of use when\Ntrouble occurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:42.90,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:44.90,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:46.90,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:48.90,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.17,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:53.96,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve come to take\Naway your trays.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:56.61,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I’ll be finished shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:13:00.52,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei, you don’t need to\Ntry to be so nice to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:02.82,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,We’re the guests here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:03.90,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.38,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,That’s all right.\NPlease take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:10.78,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Say, there’s an outdoor bath outside\Nthis room. Is it usable?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:11.74,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.06,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,You’re welcome to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.14,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:18.45,B2,PROPRIETRESS,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.98,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,The bath’s just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:32.34,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it. Rangiku is jealous\Nof the proprietress. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:36.45,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It proves how interested\Nshe is in me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.44,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no, no! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.39,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait! Calm down, Shuhei Hisagi! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.69,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We’re here on a mission. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.82,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don’t think of such perverse thoughts. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.72,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Work comes first! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.70,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get your act straight, Shuhei Hisagi! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.89,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to confirm the agenda\Nof this mission! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:55.06,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I think I’ll go for a dip\Nin the outdoor bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.24,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go for a dip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:00.17,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,In the outdoor bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:01.05,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,In the outdoor bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:01.97,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,In the outdoor bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:03.07,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,In the…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.72,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.46,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,What’s a hot spa inn\Nwithout yukata?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:25.98,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going in first, Shuhei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:27.15,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Right…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:32.41,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei, I think you already\Nknow this, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.56,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,If you peek, I’ll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.37,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.53,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Shuhei Hisagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:52.78,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let’s sort out the situation. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:55.11,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The weather worsened,\Nand the sun set. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:57.08,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By perfect coincidence,\Nthere was an inn. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.41,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, we decide to\Nstay the night. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:02.14,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, so it’s simple logic. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.14,0:15:03.68,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get it, I get it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:05.10,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was totally out\Nof my control. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:08.82,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rangiku, too, had no choice but\Nto stay the night with me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:10.32,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That has to be it. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.18,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as for the proprietress,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:15.01,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was nothing more than Rangiku showing\Nconcern for me as a colleague. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:17.78,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Rangiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:19.69,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Where is my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:22.54,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Surely we’re not going to stay\Nin the same room, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:23.79,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.90,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I asked earlier to have the\Nbedding set out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:28.28,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:35.72,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don’t want to\Nshare a room with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:37.98,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,N-N-No, that’s not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:39.55,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Then there’s no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.98,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,The water feels so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:52.64,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?\NWhy are you sighing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.43,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um… How’s the weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.34,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a lovely moon out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:15:59.91,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:03.70,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,The breeze feels nice, too.\NNothing beats an outdoor bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.40,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That’s nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:08.96,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Why don’t you come in too?\NYou must be tired, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:09.56,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:12.58,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,You haven’t taken any\Ndays off recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:17.20,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Working is fine, too, but you need to rest sometimes,\Nor you’ll wear yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:22.27,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rangiku is worried\Nabout me. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:26.05,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as I thought,\Npeople do watch! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.24,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It isn’t just Captain Hitsugaya! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.80,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rangiku understands\Nhow I feel as well! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:34.05,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’m so glad I did my best. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.39,B2,CAPTION,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WHY DON’T YOU\NCOME IN TOO?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:44.53,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She just said, “Why don’t\Nyou come in too?” {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:49.81,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does that mean…she wants\Nme to join her?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:17:00.83,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, just a moment ago, she\Nsaid she’d kill me for that. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:05.03,B2,(FROM LOOP 112),0000,0000,0000,,If you peek, I’ll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.54,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or should I not take\Nit literally? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.05,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,If you peek, I’ll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:16.45,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think I get it. Could that “I’ll kill you”\Nhave meant she was inviting me? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:21.11,B2,RANGIKU (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,I’ll…kill…you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:27.08,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no, it couldn’t\Nbe…but…but… {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.06,B2,HISAGI (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.74,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.35,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Rangiku,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.60,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I’m coming to be “killed.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:57.84,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.88,0:17:59.93,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.44,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei! Come here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:13.82,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:22.45,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,A Hollow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.89,0:18:25.52,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,This was the culprit in the\Nstring of disappearances!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.04,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:44.34,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Growl…Haineko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.79,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Reap...Kazeshini!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:17.14,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Shuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:20.05,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t get it. What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.94,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,The proprietress of this inn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:25.11,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,was the culprit responsible\Nfor the disappearances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:25.97,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:31.29,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I wasn’t certain,\Nso I came here to investigate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.99,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,only to have her suddenly\Nappear before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.94,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t see that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:39.52,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,And what’s more, she was definitely sending\Nyou some strange Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.52,0:19:40.91,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Strange Spiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.99,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Didn’t you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.13,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:46.74,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:50.66,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,You see, only men have\Nbeen attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:52.54,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Handsome ones at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:55.70,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I had you come\Nwith me as a lure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:57.22,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,It turned out to be\Nthe right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.80,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Nobody told me\Nanything about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:03.34,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,They say to deceive your enemy,\Nyou have to deceive your friend first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:07.99,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do this after Isane and the\Nothers arrived and we were set up,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:10.41,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,but the enemy snapped\Nat the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:12.52,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’s the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.49,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,That’s cruel, Rangiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:17.23,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:21.00,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,But you were the only one\Nwho could pull off this role.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:24.30,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,There aren’t any other\Ngood-looking guys with great skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:39.94,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,And you just forgave her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:43.97,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,When Rangiku said that,\NI didn’t feel bad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:47.08,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she meant that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:50.18,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she’s still pulling the\Nwool over your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:53.18,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, it’s not good\Nto be so cynical.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:54.30,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.16,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Kusajishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:58.84,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:02.67,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny busted the wall,\Ncan you help us repair it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.67,0:21:03.69,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:07.85,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Because I heard that if we ever need\Nhelp, we should ask you, Hisa-hisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:10.91,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s probably Matsumoto who’s\Nspreading that around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:12.95,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! And also…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:18.08,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei is the only person\NI can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:19.71,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:22.81,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:25.50,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,So Rangiku’s counting on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.80,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not easy being\Na talented man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.34,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hisagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:32.52,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Where’s the site! Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:39.98,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,He is hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:24.81,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Hisa-hisa sure does prove his title\Nas the Best Male Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.81,0:23:28.15,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that’s impressive.\NGuess I have a lot to learn from Hisagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:30.41,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, he is! In our last\Nladies' night out,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:33.63,B2,YACHIRU,0000,0000,0000,,he got our unanimous vote as\Nthe most useful errand boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:34.69,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s his title?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.43,B2,KON,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to\NSoul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:37.79,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.79,0:23:39.02,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Rangiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:42.42,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Can you carry these to\Nthe Squad Barracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:43.59,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Gladly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.38,0:23:46.09,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:47.02,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.30,0:23:49.00,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Stamp these for approval,\Nwill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.45,0:23:50.71,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.10,0:23:52.66,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Shuhei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.01,0:23:54.03,B2,HISAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:56.23,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,Can you wash these for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.42,0:24:03.38,B2,RANGIKU,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be losing his\Nhealth lately. I’m worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:04.43,B2,KIRA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s your fault!